title: Counting Triangles 2
text: This is a new version of problemCTwith the new limit: X, Y ≤ 10000, and the result will be written in modulo 2009InputThe input begins with C – number of test cases. Each test case consists of X, Y.OutputFor each test case, output the result in a line.LimitC ≤ 2000 ≤ X, Y ≤ 10000ExampleInput:20 31 1Output:04
